<h3>Pizza Lovers Unite!</h3>
<p>Premium Slices is a platform designed for Pizza Lovers from around the world to share their
favorite Pizza Places with one another. There's a Pizza Shop in every plaza, and every one has
the potential to be your new favorite place. Just moved? On vacation? No problem! Premium Slices
and their Pizza Brethren will make sure they hook you up with the most awesome Pizza you could
possibly think of. Whether you are in New York City or Rural Montana, Premium Slices is here to
connect you with ASTOUNDING PIZZA!</p>

<h3>It's not just the Pizza, but the history as well!</h3>

<p>Premium Slices is about more than just being a smaller yelp for Pizza Places. While we encourage
 our users to promote the great pizza that that their favorite Pizza Places make, we are also
 about the history and the memories that are made there. Every Pizza Place has a special history
  about how it came to be, and we share those stories so our users can understand the amazing amount
  of skill and hardwork that goes into making these Pizza Places as successful as they are today.</p>
